      <Link href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alifyasa"
        >https://www.linkedin.com/in/alifyasa</Link
      >.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      Gmail.
      <Link href="mailto:malifputrayasa@gmail.com">malifputrayasa@gmail.com</Link>.
